data.description: Beautiful Lake Arlington home in Enchanted Bay. This home is zoned to the highly sought after Martin High School. The home has 5 bedrooms 3.5 baths and a 2 car garage. This Open concept home has a breathtaking entry and beautiful hardwood and tile flooring. Front left bedroom could double as an office or study. Formal dining room for holidays and  family gatherings as well as a formal living room! Large primary bedroom is split. The primary bathroom offering a dual rainfall shower and regular shower head. Separate garden tub and huge walk-in closet. Kitchen offers stainless steel double ovens and a gas cooktop for those who love to cook with an open view to the family room. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms 2 full bathrooms. Enjoy the game room with views of beautiful Lake Arlington. Owner had concrete poured for additional parking(RVs, boats, etc.).The seller is willing to remove the concrete for a buyer preferring more yard. Remote controlled electric gate added for privacy.
